Root Tag

HTML
Html stands for hyper text markup language used for showing enclosed data in tags on web
it helps to tell to browse that how to show enclosed text on web
it helps to create the structure of web page or website but simple
it is not case sensitive language there all cases accepted


Html consists of tags. tags can be categorised as
1.paired tags/container tags
it consists of start and end tag
2.emplty/singelton/non container tag:
it consists of only start tag no end tag

Attributes in html:
it helps to enhance the appearnce of text enclosed in tags
it can come under container as well as empty

horizontal ruler<hr>
break a line<br>
paragraph<p></p>
hyperlink <a href="" target="_blank"></>

==>Image tag
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<title>First Wweb Page</title>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>Hello Everyone</h1>
<img style="height: 300px;width: 400px;border-radius: 40px;" src="img2.jpg"></img>
</body>
</html>


==>To create a table

<table>
<tr>
<th></th>
<tr>
<td></td>
</tr>

<html>

<head>
<title></title>
</head>

<body>
</body>
</html>

==mAKE  a page having headers, text styles, fonts ==>

<html>

<head>
<title>First Web Page</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="cyan" text="red">
<h1>The quick brown fox jumps over the little lazy dog</h1>
<h2>The quick brown fox jumps over the little lazy dog</h2>
<h3>The quick brown fox jumps over the little lazy dog</h3>
<h4>The quick brown fox jumps over the little lazy dog</h4>
<h5>The quick brown fox jumps over the little lazy dog</h5>
<h6>The quick brown fox jumps over the little lazy dog</h6>
<hr>
<br>
<font color="blue" size="16">
<b>This text will be in bold</b><br>
<i>This text will be in italic</i><br>
<u>This is underlined text</u>
</font>
</body>
</html>



== list in html======

<html>

<head>
<title>Lists and Pre</title>
</head>
<body>
<ul>
	<li> Apple </li>
	<li> Orange </li>
	<li> Mango </li>
	<li> Banana </li>
	<li> Grapes </li>

</ul>
<ol>
	<li> Apple </li>
	<li> Orange </li>
	<li> Mango </li>
	<li> Banana </li>
	<li> Grapes </li>

</ol>
</body>
</html>


















